ntent":"Please plan for your business; we can help you do it right.","_id":"7cc3a2d"},{"tab_title":"How are SDLC developers of cryptocurrency different?","tab_content":"At SDLC, we carefully check out our developers to ensure we only connect you with the best people. As a result, less than 3% of the more than 100,000 people who apply each year to join the SDLC network are accepted. You'll work with engineers, not general recruiters or HR reps, to figure out your goals, technical needs, and how your team works. The result is talent from our network that has been screened by experts and is a perfect fit for your business.\n&nbsp;","_id":"0bde77c"},{"tab_title":"How long do cryptocurrency developers have to try SDLC without taking risks?","tab_content":"Each time you hire a new programmer from us, you'll have the opportunity to give them a test run for up to two weeks before committing to them permanently. This means you have time to make sure that the engagement will work. If the repair has been completed to your satisfaction, Time spent on this project will be billed to you, and we'll stay on the job for as long as you need us. Payment is required only if you are satisfied with the service provided. From there, we can either go our separate ways or find you another expert who might be a better fit and start a second, risk-free trial with them.","_id":"9ef9b95"},{"tab_title":"Can I find cryptocurrency developers through SDLC in less than 48 hours?","tab_content":"<p>You could start working with a developer 48 hours after signing up, depending on their availability and how quickly you can make progress.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","_id":"8e9bd38"},{"tab_title":"How will I know how my cryptocurrency project is coming on through?","tab_content":"<ul><li>Your project will be handed to a PROJECT MANAGER.<\/li><li>You can talk to the Project manager directly once a week to find out how things are going.<\/li><li>A Skype\/WhatsApp group will be made to share the news.<\/li><li>We'll